17;un site, d&#8217;un e-commerce, d&#8217;une plateforme d&#8217;offres&#8230;Dans cet article, nous d\u00e9couvrirons comment utiliser efficacement le potentiel de cet outil, tout en \u00e9vitant le pire. Nous aborderons \u00e9galement les concepts cl\u00e9s tels que le <strong>searchdexing<\/strong>, les facettes, l&#8217;indexation, ou le <strong>contenu g\u00e9n\u00e9r\u00e9 par les utilisateurs<\/strong> (UGC).<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/moteur-recherche-interne.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Moteur Recherche Interne\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/moteur-recherche-interne.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/moteur-recherche-interne-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/moteur-recherche-interne-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/moteur-recherche-interne-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"htt